%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Housing%20keeps%20getting%20less%20affordable%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20math%20only%20improved%20in%20one%20major%20city%20this%20year%2C%20says%20Redfin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20real%20estate%20agent%20holding%20a%20house%20key%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65727f887a3c8094d5dae02d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERedfin%20expects%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20dip%20next%20year.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMedian%20income%20earners%20spent%2041%25%20of%20their%20pay%20on%20housing%20this%20year%2C%20up%20from%2021%25%20in%202012%2C%20per%20Redfin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnly%20Austin%2C%20Texas%20bucked%20the%20trend%20of%20declining%20affordability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20Anaheim%20and%20San%20Francisco%2C%20many%20homebuyers%20can%20expect%20to%20spend%2080%25%20of%20their%20income%20on%20housing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20home%20for%20many%20people%20has%20never%20been%20less%20affordable%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20real%20estate%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fnews%2Fhousing-affordability-at-record-low-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERedfin%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20median%20income%20earner%20would%20need%20to%20spend%2041%25%20of%20their%20earnings%20on%20monthly%20housing%20costs%20if%20they'd%20bought%20a%20median-priced%20home%2C%20per%20Redfin's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20close%20to%20double%20the%20level%20in%202012%2C%20when%20Redfin%20started%20collecting%20data%2C%20and%20a%20big%20jump%20from%2031%25%20just%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedfin's%20analysis%20calculated%20monthly%20housing%20payments%20using%20median%20home%20prices%2C%20average%20mortgage%20rates%20of%206.73%25%2C%20and%20median%20incomes%2C%20considering%20a%2020%