0Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20specific%20case%2C%20yes%20on%20the%20Parliament%2C%20we%20are%20caught%20in%20a%20bind%20here.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20amplify%20or%20give%20too%20much%20of%20credence%20to%20such%20extremists%20who%20make%20threats%20and%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20coverage.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20we%20take%20this%20seriously%2C%20in%20this%20particular%20case%20I%20know%20that%20we%20have%20taken%20up%20this%20matter%20with%20the%20US%20and%20Canadian%20authorities%20about%20this%20threat%2C%20but%20as%20I%20said%2C%20extremists%20and%20terrorists%20have%20a%20tendency%20of%20wanting%20media%20coverage%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20dignify%20them%20that%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702005591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30123119%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20arrested%20in%20France%20over%20alleged%20bedbug%20scam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702005505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F73D7%2Fproduction%2F_131955692_5ba410fc1cb003ce08651e9ff6b2b45635ce66aa0_0_2300_15341000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67655992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20in%20Strasbourg%20say%20the%20men%20charged%20victims%20thousands%20of%20euros%20for%20pest%20control%20they%20did%20not%20need.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag