tv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-chandrashekar-rao-hospitalised-after-fall-may-require-surgery-4644452%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20Does%20Just%20Enough%20To%20Hold%20Kadak%20Singh%20Together%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeldom%20does%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme%20investigator%20face%20a%20test%20as%20stern%20as%20the%20one%20that%20the%20amiable%20but%20unyielding%20protagonist%20of%20%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20up%20against.%20He%20is%20a%20man%20with%20a%20past%20but%20with%20no%20memory%20of%20it.%20As%20he%20recuperates%20in%20a%20hospital%2C%20he%20takes%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20put%20the%20scattered%20pieces%20back%20together%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20reminiscences%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Award-winning%20director%20Aniruddha%20Roy%20Chowdhury's%20third%20Hindi%20film%20(after%20%3Ci%3EPink%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20%3Ci%3ELost%3C%2Fi%3E)%20centres%20on%20a%20now%20on%2C%20now%20off%20investigation%20into%20a%20chit%20fund%20scam%20that%20has%20cleaned%20out%20countless%20lower%20middle-class%20investors.%20It%20is%20a%20veritable%20jigsaw%20puzzle%20with%20large%20pieces%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20the%20missing%20millions%20isn't%20unusual%20nor%20is%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20is%20presented.%20It%20is%20the%20fragile%20psyche%20of%20the%20sleuth%20that%20sets%20the%20procedural%20apart%20from%20others%20of%20its%20kind.%20But%20the%20slow%20and%20steady%20%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%20isn't%20the%20sort%20of%20whodunit%20that%20will%20zap%20you%20out%20of%20your%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScripted%20by%20Ritesh%20Shah%20with%20a%20story%20written%20by%20him%20with%20the%20director%20and%20Viraf%20Sarkari%2C%20employs%20a%20fragmentary%2C%20multiple-perspective%20structure%20in%20which%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20is%20viewed%20and%20processed%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20four%20characters.%20It%20reaches%20its%20conclusion%20when%20the%20protagonist%20has%20heard%20enough%20to%20be%20able%20to%20offset%20his%20memory%20blackout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20streaming%20on%20Zee5%2C%20moves%20back%20and%20forth%20in%20time%20and%20space.%20It%20gives%20the%20impression%20of%20being%20repetitive%20and%20circuitous.%20A%20set%20of%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20man%20up%20close%20-%20his%20daughter%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20colleagues%20and%20a%20friend%20-%20provide%20their%20individual%20perceptions%20of%20the%20protagonist%2C%20Arun%20Kumar%20(AK)%20Srivastava%20(Pankaj%20Tripathi)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAK%2C%20an%20officer%20with%20the%20Kolkata%20unit%20of%20a%20financial%20crime%20investigation%20agency%2C%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20retrograde%20amnesia.%20He%20is%20unable%20to%20recognise%20people%20around%20him%20or%20recollect%20the%20details%20of%20the%20probe%20that%20he%20was%20spearheading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delicate%20state%20of%20his%20mind%20is%20a%20result%20of%20neurological%20damage%20caused%20by%20an%20alleged%20suicide%20attempt.%20But%20what%20exactly%20happened%20on%20the%20day%20that%20AK%20was%20wheeled%20into%20a%20hospital%20is%20shrouded%20in%20mystery.%20He%20obviously%20remembers%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAK%20is%20in%20the%20capable%20hands%20of%20the%20hospital's%20hawk-eyed%2C%20chatty%20head%20nurse%20Miss%20Kannan%20(Parvathy%20Thiruvothu)%2C%20the%20only%20person%20in%20his%20immediate%20circle%20he%20now%20recognises%20because%20she%20is%20part%20of%20his%20current%20reality.%20Everybody%20else%20has%20receded%20to%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20widower's%20daughter%2C%20his%20boss%2C%20a%20trusted%20younger%20co-worker%20and%20a%20woman%20he%20is%20in%20a%20steady%20relationship%20with%20visit%20his%20ward%20one%20by%20one%20-%20he%20has%20no%20idea%20anymore%20who%20they%20are.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20falls%20back%20on%20the%20'stories'%20that%20they%20narrate%20to%20try%20and%20figure%20out%20who%20he%20is%20and%20how%20he%20has%20ended%20up%20in%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20opening%20moments%20of%20%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20AK%20saunters%20into%20a%20seedy%20suburban%20hotel%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20a%20younger%20woman.%20There%2C%20he%20chances%20upon%20a%20girl%20(Sanjana%20Sanghi)%2C%20who%20is%20visibly%20startled%20on%20seeing%20him.%20She%20flees%20from%20the%20precincts.%20Arun%20pursues%20her%20out%20of%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20the%20hospital%20bed%2C%20where%20AK%20has%20a%20visitor.%20It%20is%20the%20girl%20he%20ran%20into%20in%20the%20first%20sequence.%20She%20introduces%20herself%20as%20his%20daughter%20Sakshi.%20AK%20looks%20at%20her%20blankly.%20He%20asserts%20that%20he%20has%20only%20one%20child%20-%20a%20five-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nonplussed%20girl%20tells%20AK%20that%20he%20is%20mistaken.%20He%20does%20indeed%20have%20a%20son%20but%20he%20is%20now%20a%20teenager.%20She%20narrates%20her%20story%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20jog%20his%20'memory'%20and%20convince%20him%20that%20she%20is%20his%20biological%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20even%20tells%20him%20why%20he%20is%20Kadak%20Singh%20for%20his%20children.%20Scrupulous%20to%20a%20fault%20and%20a%20perfectionist%20who%20has%20no%20patience%20for%20slip-ups%2C%20he%20lets%20those%20traits%20affect%20his%20style%20of%20parenting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20begins%20a%20series%20of%20interactions.%20Naina%20(Jaya%20Ahsan)%2C%20a%20woman%20Arun%20has%20been%20in%20love%20with%20presumably%20since%20before%20the%20time%20he%20lost%20his%20wife%20in%20an%20accident%20that%20his%20children%20hold%20him%20responsible%20for%2C%20is%20the%20next%20visitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FzP0AsKwd_Fo%3Fsi%3D_MrfjF6X4Pkgw2Jf%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20provides%20another%20window%20on%20a%20past%20that%20has%20been%20wiped%20clean%20from%20AK's%20mind.%20Naina's%20recollections%2C%20like%20those%20of%20the%20others%20who%20call%20on%20him%20in%20subsequent%20scenes%2C%20help%20him%20dispel%20the%20fadeout%20he%20has%20suffered%2C%20besides%20aiding%20the%20audience%20in%20understanding%20what%20is%20going%20on%20with%20and%20around%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAK's%20boss%20Jitender%20Tyagi%20(Dilip%20Shankar)%20turns%20up%20next%20followed%20soon%20after%20by%20another%20colleague%20from%20the%20department%2C%20Arjun%20(Paresh%20Pahuja)%2C%20a%20man%20referred%20to%20by%20AK's%20children%20as%20%26quot%3Basli%20beta%26quot%3B%20so%20fond%20is%20he%20of%20him.%20From%20their%20separate%20mist-lifting%20perspectives%2C%20the%20two%20men%20recall%20what%20transpired%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20incident%20that%20ended%20with%20AK%20being%20rushed%20to%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20family%20drama%2C%20a%20white-collar%20crime%20story%20and%20an%20investigative%20thriller.%20It%20isn't%20the%20sort%20of%20pulsating%2C%20edge-of-the-seat%20fare%20that%20one%20would%20go%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20to%20watch%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20few%20passages%20that%20work%20well%20enough%20to%20be%20mildly%20diverting%2C%20thanks%20particularly%20to%20Pankaj%20Tripathi's%20restrained%2C%20if%20somewhat%20limited%2C%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mystery%20of%20AK's%20hospitalisation%20revolves%20around%20his%20quirky%2C%20difficult%20to%20gauge%20demeanour%2C%20which%20often%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20is%20there%20more%20to%20his%20behaviour%20than%20meets%20the%20eye%3F%20What%20are%20the%20answers%20that%20his%20memory%20loss%20conceals%20that%20he%20must%20find%20in%20order%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20maze%20that%20the%20sudden%20turn%20of%20events%20has%20pushed%20him%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20muted%20methods%20notwithstanding%2C%20%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%20does%2C%20at%20times%2C%20spring%20to%20life%2C%20riding%20on%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20case%20that%20AK%20was%20investigating%20until%20its%20progress%20was%20interrupted%20and%20the%20surprises%20springing%20from%20the%20acts%20of%20remembering%20and%20forgetting%20and%20forming%20linkages%20between%20disparate%20shards%20of%20memory%20that%20begin%20to%20coalesce%20little%20by%20little%20and%20take%20the%20form%20of%20a%20coherent%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20that%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%20plays%20does%20not%20push%20him%20out%20of%20his%20comfort%20zone%20but%20he%20does%20just%20enough%20to%20hold%20the%20film%20together.%20The%20actors%20around%20him%20-%20Jaya%20Ahsan%2C%20Sanjana%20Sanghi%2C%20Dilip%20Shankar%20and%20Paresh%20Pahuja%20-%20have%20largely%20reactive%20roles%2C%20confined%20as%20they%20are%20to%20closed%20spaces%20physically%20and%20creatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20outright%20humdrum%2C%20%3Ci%3EKadak%20Singh%3C%2Fi%3E%20would%20have%20had%20far%20greater%20tensile%20energy%20had%20its%20edges%20been%20sharper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702005000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fphjof308_-kadak-singh_625x300_08_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkadak-singh-review-pankaj-tripathi-does-just-enough-to-hold-the-film-together-2-5-stars-4644473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kadak%20Singh%20Review%3A%20The%20actors%20around%20him%20-%20Jaya%20Ahsan%2C%20Sanjana%20Sanghi%2C%20Dilip%20Shankar%20and%20Paresh%20Pahuja%20-%20have%20largely%20reactive%20roles%2C%20confined%20as%20they%20are%20to%20closed%20spaces%20physically%20and%20creatively.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkadak-singh-review-pankaj-tripathi-does-just-enough-to-hold-the-film-together-2-5-stars-4644473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%