c-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67647452.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67647452.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden's%20Son%20Hunter%20Indicted%20On%20Federal%20Tax%20Evasion%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHunter%20Biden%20was%20indicted%20late%20Thursday%20on%20multiple%20counts%20of%20tax%20evasion%2C%20the%20second%20time%20this%20year%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20troubled%20son%20has%20been%20charged%20by%20a%20special%20counsel%20investigating%20his%20personal%20and%20business%20dealings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHunter%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20in%20a%20four-year%20scheme%20to%20not%20pay%20at%20least%20%241.4%20million%20in%20self-assessed%20federal%20taxes%20he%20owed%20for%20tax%20years%202016%20through%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20special%20counsel%20David%20Weiss%20said%20in%20the%2056-page%20indictment%20filed%20in%20US%20district%20court%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20charged%20with%20nine%20counts%20of%20failing%20to%20file%20and%20pay%20taxes%2C%20tax%20evasion%20and%20filing%20false%20tax%20returns%2C%20the%20indictment%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20charges%20serve%20up%20more%20acute%20embarrassment%20for%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20he%20wages%20an%20uphill%20battle%20for%20reelection%20and%20fends%20off%20a%20Republican%20bid%20to%20impeach%20him%20on%20grounds%20that%20he%20benefitted%20from%20his%20son's%20overseas%20business%20dealings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20charges%20accuse%20the%20younger%20Biden%20of%20lying%20about%20his%20drug%20use%20on%20a%20federal%20application%20when%20he%20purchased%20a%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20charges%20mean%20that%20Hunter%20Biden%20could%20in%20theory%20go%20on%20trial%20twice%20next%20year%20as%20his%20father%20almost%20certainly%20faces%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20has%20insisted%20he%20stands%20by%20his%20son%20despite%20his%20past%20troubled%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20indictment%20says%20Hunter%20Biden%20earned%20more%20than%20%247%20million%20from%202016%20to%202020%20and%20used%20this%20money%20for%20a%20freewheeling%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendant%20spent%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20an%20extravagant%20lifestyle%20at%20the%20same%20time%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20pay%20his%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20indictment%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BBetween%202016%20and%20October%2015%2C%202020%2C%20the%20defendant%20spent%20this%20money%20on%20drugs%2C%20escorts%20and%20girlfriends%2C%20luxury%20hotels%20and%20rental%20properties%2C%20exotic%20cars%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20other%20items%20of%20a%20personal%20nature%2C%20in%20short%2C%20everything%20but%20his%20taxes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHunter%20Biden%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20this%20year%20to%20three%20felony%20charges%20stemming%20from%20his%20purchase%20of%20a%20.38-caliber%20Colt%20Cobra%20revolver%20in%202018%20when%2C%20by%20his%20own%20admission%2C%20he%20was%20addicted%20to%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20charged%20with%20illegally%20possessing%20the%20handgun%20and%20two%20counts%20of%20making%20false%20statements%20for%20claiming%20on%20forms%20required%20for%20the%20gun%20purchase%20that%20he%20was%20not%20using%20drugs%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20opened%20an%20impeachment%20inquiry%20in%20Congress%20into%20what%20they%20claim%20is%20a%20Biden%20family%20criminal%20conspiracy%20but%20have%20provided%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20president%20did%20anything%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20plea%20bargain%20between%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20prosecutor%20Weiss%20--%20which%20would%20have%20erased%20the%20gun%20charges%20while%20Biden%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20two%20tax%20charges%20and%20avoided%20prison%20--%20fell%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHunter%20Biden%20h