3EDavid%20Wolpe%2C%20a%20rabbi%20and%20visiting%20scholar%20at%20Harvard%20Divinity%20School%2C%20resigned%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-penn-mit-presidents-statements-antisemitism-genocide-congress-testimony-backlash-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20University's%20antisemitism%3C%2Fa%3E%20advisory%20committee%2C%20he%20announced%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolpe's%20resignation%20came%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvard-mit-upenn-college-presidents-response-jewish-genocide-antisemitism-israel-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20President%20Claudine%20Gay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20MIT%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20testified%20before%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20presidents%20drew%20widespread%20criticism%20for%20their%20responses%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20calling%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%20of%20Jews%26quot%3B%20is%20considered%20harassment%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20institution's%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20Gay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRabbiWolpe%2Fstatus%2F1732847411175796747%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20his%20resignation%2C%20Wolpe%20said%20Gay's%20testimony%20factored%20into%20his%20decision%20to%20resign%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bboth%20events%20on%20campus%20and%20the%20painfully%20inadequate%20testimony%20reinforced%20the%20idea%20that%20I%20cannot%20make%20the%20sort%20of%20difference%20I%20had%20hoped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolpe%20said%20he%20believed%20%26quot%3BClaudine%20Gay%20to%20be%20both%20a%20kind%20and%20thoughtful%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20there%20are%20many%20good%20people%20at%20Harvard%2C%20and%20that%20the%20institution%20is%20%26quot%3