0life.%20The%20longest%20I%20could%20clean%20in%20the%20vacuum's%20standard%20mode%20was%20about%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%20that%20was%20only%20on%20easy%20cleaning%20jobs%20like%20picking%20up%20dirt%20from%20the%20hardwood%20floor.%20Shark%20advertises%2060%20minutes%20of%20battery%20life%20in%20Eco%20mode%20when%20using%20the%20vacuum%20as%20a%20handheld%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20even%20get%2015%20minutes%20of%20battery%20life%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20shark%20stratos%20cleaning%20flour%20on%20carpet%20and%20hard%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a2c0a58e7c0c29a28d965%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20easily%20picked%20up%20flour%20on%20hardwood%20and%20carpet%20on%20all%20three%20power%20modes.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20is%20about%20as%20simple%20as%20it%20gets.%20The%20model's%20lack%20of%20a%20cord%20and%20easy%20maneuverability%20make%20it%20a%20fantastic%20choice%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20a%20clunky%20vacuum.%20Both%20the%20full-size%20and%20handheld%20versions%20of%20this%20vacuum%20were%20also%20convenient%20to%20use%20at%20all%20times%20of%20day%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20LED%20headlights%20that%20illuminate%20the%20floor.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20bendable%20stick%20and%20swivel%20head%2C%20the%20vacuum%20has%20a%20press%20button%20to%20control%20its%20power%20and%20mode%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20this%20saves%20you%20from%20applying%20constant%20pressure%20to%20a%20power%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20has%20three%20modes%20for%20cleaning%3A%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%2C%20Eco%2C%20and%20Boost%20mode.%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%20is%20what%20I%20primarily%20tested%2C%20as%20this%20is%20the%20power%20mode%20that's%20most%20suited%20for%20general%20cleaning.%20It%20uses%20an%20infrared%20sensor%20to%20increase%20or%20decrease%20power%20depending%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20debris%20it's%20picking%20up.%20Eco%20mode%20lowers%20power%20to%20save%20battery%2C%20although%20there%20wasn't%20much%20difference%20in%20power%20performance%20during%20our%20tests%20on%20this%20mode.%20Boost%20mode%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20cleaning%20option%2C%20increases%20power%20during%20cleaning.%20This%20mode%20is%20best%20suited%20for%20heavy%20vacuuming%20jobs%20or%20picking%20up%20larger%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20vacuum%20on%20hardfloor%20vacuuming%20kibble.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a2c4958e7c0c29a28d99f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20vacuum%20excels%20at%20cleaning%20larger%20debris%20like%20kibble%20and%20bits%20of%20plastic%2C%20which%20is%20unusual%20for%20a%20cordless%20vacuum%20model.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3ECleaning%20performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20hardwood%20and%20carpet%20vacuuming%2C%20this%20vacuum%20performed%20well.%20It%20excels%20at%20picking%20up%20oversize%20debris%20items%20and%20does%20so%20much%20better%20than%20my%20upright%20vacuum%20can.%20This%20model%20also%20picks%20up%20hair%20without%20getting%20it%20tangled%20in%20the%20brush%20roll%2C%20which%20I%20was%20thrilled%20by.%20The%20Shark%20Stratos%20struggled%20to%20clean%20especially%20fine%20materials%20like%20sand%20and%20sugar%20on%20the%20first%20pass%2C%20but%20one%20or%20two%20runs%20over%20this%20type%20of%20debris%20in%20the%20Boost%20mode%20(the%20most%20powerful%20mode%20on%20this%20model)%20cleaned%20it%20right%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20uses%20an%20infrared%20sensor%20when%20in%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%20mode%20to%20increas