disgrace-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBillionaire%20Bill%20Ackman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20for%20the%20three%20presidents%20to%20%26quot%3Bresign%20in%20disgrace%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagill%20later%20released%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresident.upenn.edu%2Fcontent%2Fvideo-message-president-magill-congressional-hearing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20video%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%207%20p.m.%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20after%20an%20online%20uproar%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-president-letter-israel-antisemitism-tweets-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Euniversity's%20policies%20on%20free%20speech%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20harassment%20into%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20our%20university's%20longstanding%20policies%20aligned%20with%20the%20US%20Constitution%2C%20which%20say%20that%20speech%20alone%20is%20not%20punishable%2C%26quot%3B%20Magill%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20focused%20on%2C%20but%20I%20should%20have%20been%2C%20the%20irrefutable%20fact%20that%20a%20call%20for%20genocide%20of%20Jewish%20people%20is%20a%20call%20for%20some%20of%20the%20most%20terrible%20violence%20human%20beings%20can%20perpetrate.%20It's%20evil%20%E2%80%94%20plain%20and%20simple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20letter%20Stevens%20sent%20to%20his%20staff%20at%20Stone%20Ridge%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3ETeam%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20want%20to%20briefly%20discuss%20three%20topics%20that%20may%20seem%20unrelated%3A%201)%20discrimination%20and%20harassment%2C%202)%20philanthropy%2C%20and%203)%20institutional%20neutrality.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFirst%2C%20every%20year%20we%20hold%20New%20York%20State-required%20firmwide%20discrimination%20and%20harassment%20training.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20those%20sessions%2C%20many%20of%20you%20will%20remember%20that%20my%20closing%20remarks%20are%20always%20a%20version%20of%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20almost%20nothing%20that%20will%20get%20you%20walked%20out%20of%20Stone%20Ridge%20on%20a%20first%20offense%2C%20but%20discrimination%20or%20harassment%20is%20one%20of%20those%20things%20and%20I%20will%20do%20it%20myself.%20Zero%20exceptions%2C%20zero%20tolerance.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20treating%20each%20other%20with%20kindness%20has%20been%20a%20foundational%20principle%2C%20and%20a%20non-negotiable%2C%20since%20the%20firm%20began.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESecond%2C%20as%20I've%20privately%20shared%20at%20several%20firmwide%20meetings%2C%20my%20personal%20approach%20to%20philanthropy%20focuses%20on%20how%20the%20multiplier%20effect%20of%20educational%20excellence%2C%20economic%20liberty%2C%20and%20free%20markets%20can%20transform%20lives.%20In%20addition%2C%20my%20wife%20Deb%20and%20I%20have%20chosen%20to%20donate%20anonymously%2C%20except%20for%20educational%20causes.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EYou%20almost%20certainly%20do%20not%20know%20that%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20(%26quot%3BPenn%26quot%3B)%20currently%20holds%20shares%20in%20Stone%20Ridge%20Holdings%20Group%20worth%20approximately%20%24100%20million.%20Given%20the%20bedrock%20importance%20of%20firm%20culture%2C%20I%20inserted%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20founding%20documents%20of%20our%20partnership%20agreement%20that%20permits%20me%20to%20rescind%20the%20shares%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%2C%20simply%20cancel%20them%20%E2%80%93%20of%20any%20shareholder%20that%20violates%20our%20firm's%20rules%20in%20a%20way%20that%20injures%20our%20business%2C%20reputation%2C%20character%2C%20or%20standing.%20I%20have%20never%20had%20to%20invoke%20these%20provisions%20before%20and%20never%20thought%20I%20would.%20Until%20now.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOver%20the%20past%20months%2C%20Penn%20President%20Liz%20Magill%20has%20enabled%20and%20encouraged%20antisemitism%20and%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%20and%20harassment%20at%20Penn.%20Further%2C%20at%20a%20congressional%20hearing%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20Ms.%20Magill%20made%20clear%20her%20personal%20view%20that%20any%20Penn%20professors%20and%20students%20who%20call%20for%20genocide%20against%20Jews%20do%20not%20violate%20Penn's%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20As%20a%20proud%20Penn%20alum%2C%20as%20father%20of%20a%20recent%20Penn%20grad%2C%20also%20of%20a%20current%20junior%2C%20and%20on%20behalf%20of%20my%20beloved%20University%2C%20I%20can%20state%20without%20equivocation%20that%20Liz%20Magill%20is%20wrong.%20Calls%20for%20genocide%20against%20any%20group%20do%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20violate%20Penn's%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%20More%20importantly%2C%20such%20calls%20most%20definitely%20violate%20Stone%20Ridge's%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20have%20clear%20grounds%20to%20rescind%20Penn's%20%24100%20million%20of%20Stone%20Ridge%20shares%20due%20to%20the%20conduct%20of%20President%20Magill.%20Stone%20Ridge%20outside%20counsel%20at%20Davis%20Polk%20have%20sent%20Penn%20a%20letter%20detailing%20their%20violations.%20At%20risk%20of%20stating%20the%20absolutely%20obvious%2C%20any%20employee%20of%20Stone%20Ridge%20that%20made%20equivalently%20discriminatory%20statements%20about%20any%20group%20would%20be%20immediately%20terminated%20for%20cause.%20By%20me.%20%3Cstrong%3EAbsent%20a%20change%20in%20leadership%20and%20values%20at%20Penn%20in%20the%20very%20near%20future%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20rescind%20Penn's%20Stone%20Ridge%20shares%20to%20prevent%20any%20further%20reputational%20and%20other%20damage%20to%20Stone%20Ridge%20as%20a%20result%20of%20our%20relationship%20with%20Penn%20and%20Liz%20Magill.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20love%20Penn%20and%20it%20is%20important%20to%20me%2C%20but%20our%20firm's%20principles%20are%20more%20important.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThird%20and%20finally%2C%20at%20Stone%20Ridge%20we%20manage%20the%20firm%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BChicago%20Principles%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20include%20the%20concept%20of%20institutional%20neutrality.%20That's%20a%20fancy%20way%20of%20saying%20I%20never%20comment%20on%20current%20events%20in%20my%20official%20capacity%20as%20CEO.%20That%20approach%20has%20aged%20well%20for%20my%20other%20beloved%20alma%20mater%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20and%20it%20has%20aged%20well%20for%20us%20at%20Stone%20Ridge.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20institutional%20neutrality%20is%20vital%20for%20firm%20culture%2C%20helps%20foster%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%2C%20and%20facilitates%20laser%20focus%20on%20our%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3Ebusiness%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20mission%3A%20financial%20security%20for%20all.%20Beyond%20its%20inherent%20moral%20value%2C%20institutional%20neutrality%20is%20a%20critical%20ingredient%20for%20groundbreaking%20innovation%20in%20both%20academia%20and%20business.%20It%20has%20certainly%20worked%20for%20us.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWarmly%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ERoss%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fross-stevens-letter-pull-penn-donation-president-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701989206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657247650ec98e92f74d5acd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fross-stevens-letter-pull-penn-donation-president-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20letter%20to%20staff%2C%20Ross%20Stevens%20detailed%20why%20he%20may%20pull%20a%20%24100%20million%20gift%20to%20Penn%20following%20its%20president's%20congressional%20testimony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg%2CJordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fross-stevens-letter-pull-pen