%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20players%20are%20eliminated%20on%20the%20show%2C%20they%20obviously%20don't%20die%20like%20in%20the%20original%20drama.%20Rather%2C%20a%20splash%20of%20black%20ink%20explodes%20across%20their%20chest%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20frequently%2C%20they%20pantomime%20falling%20to%20the%20ground%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20create%20the%20effect%2C%20players%20wore%20a%20vest%20underneath%20their%20t-shirts%20and%20tracksuits%20that%20contained%20air%20canisters%20and%20the%20nozzle%20from%20which%20the%20ink%20would%20explode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20effect%20also%20involved%20what%20the%20players%20were%20wearing%20on%20top.%20Costume%20designer%20Rikki%20Finlay%20explained%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20they%20had%20to%20strip%20the%20players'%20t-shirts%20of%20starch%20by%20immersing%20them%20in%20vinegar%20and%20washing%20them.%20Doing%20so%20allowed%20the%20ink%20to%20burst%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutive%20producer%20Stephen%20Yemoh%20explained%20that%20the%20black%20ink%20was%20a%20reference%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20squid%20ink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20guards%20were%20trained%20on%20how%20to%20move%20and%20act.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22squid%20game%20guards%20wearing%20pink%20junpsuits%20and%20masks%20with%20circles%20and%20squares%20on%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657215060ec98e92f74d393c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20guards%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYemoh%20explained%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20the%20actors%20playing%20the%20game's%20guards%20trained%20with%20a%20choreographer%2C%20who%20ensured%20that%20they%20all%20walked%20and%20stood%20in%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENew%20games%20were%20meant%20to%20illustrate%2C%20and%20riff%20on%2C%20the%20interpersonal%20tension%20between%20players.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22squid%20game%20the%20challenge%20players%20sitting%20in%20a%20circle%20at%20school%20desks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657210207a3c8094d5dab49e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20contestants%20play%20circle%20of%20trust.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20drama%2C%20producers%20couldn't%20write%20out%20the%20drama%20and%20tension%20that%20makes%20good%20television.%20Instead%2C%20they%20had%20to%20use%20new%20games%20in%20order%20to%20up%20the%20ante%20among%20the%20contestants%2C%20executive%20producer%20Stephen%20Lambert%20said%20in%20the%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20moments%20where%20individuals%20or%20groups%20of%20people%20are%20asked%20to%20make%20very%20difficult%20decisions%20that%20test%20their%20morality%2C%20also%20their%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20executive%20producer%20Tim%20Harcourt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20doll%20was%203D%20printed.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20large%20doll%20in%20squid%20game%20the%20challenge%2C%20a%20chlidlike%20figure%20with%20a%20yellow%20shirt%2C%20orange%20dress%2C%20and%20pigtails%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572038e7a3c8094d5daacae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20doll%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20the%20doll%20(also%20known%20by%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BYoung-hee%26quot%3B)%20was%20modeled%20after%20the%20one%20in%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToni%20Ireland%2C%20an%20executive%20producer%2C%20said%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20the%20doll%20was%20made%20using%203D%20printing%2C%20and%20has%20mechanical%20elements%20that%20allow%20her%20head%20to%20rotate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20used%20motion-tracking%20technology%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20cameras.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowd%20in%20green%20running%20across%20a%20room%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657203bb58e7c0c29a2aafc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green.%20Light%26quot%3B%20game%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBryn%20Williams%2C%20the%20games%20technical%20consultant%20on%20the%20show%2C%20said%20that%20the%20team%20developed%20the%20motion-tracking%20software%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20game%20by%20first%20building%20a%20simulator%20that%20could%20handle%20the%20scale%20of%20a%20456-player%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20contestant%20was%20wearing%20a%20tracker%20during%20the%20game%2C%20Ireland%20said.%20There%20were%2016%20cameras%20observing%20the%20players%20looking%20for%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIreland%20explained%20that%20when%20it%20came%20down%20to%20deciding%20eliminations%2C%20the%20show's%20adjudicators%20would%20vet%20all%20%26quot%3Bevents%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20any%20ambiguous%20motions%20on%20the%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnlike%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20players%20don't%20play%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20on%20sand.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22squid%20game%20players%20running%20while%20playing%20red%20light%20green%20light%2C%20all%20wearing%20green%20track%20suits%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572059158e7c0c29a2ab141%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlayers%20race%20during%20%26quot%3BRed%20Light%2C%20Green%20Light%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EArt%20director%20Luke%20Fuller%20explained%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20sand%20would%20have%20set%20off%20the%20motion%20detectors%20as%20players%20kicked%20it%20up.%20Instead%2C%20the%20production%20put%20down%20a%20carpet%20that%20looked%20like%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20player%20bathrooms%20were%20made%20partially%20from%20custom-colored%20tiles.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22squid%20game%20the%20challenge%20players%20brush%20their%20teeth%20at%20sinks%20in%20a%20brightly%20colored%20%20blue%20and%20cream%20tiled%20bathroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657214807a3c8094d5dab753%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20tiles%20on%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%3A%20The%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20were%20custom%20ordered.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20having%20to%20make%20the%20shower%20and%20toilet%20spaces%20functional%20compared%20to%20the%20original%20drama%2C%20the%20production%20also%20had%20a%20difficult%20time%20exactly%20replicating%20the%20look%20of%20the%20bathrooms%20in%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArt%20director%20Luke%20Fuller%20said%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20it%20was%20particularly%20difficult%20to%20get%20the%20right%20colors%20for%20the%20bathroom%20tiles.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20production%20ended%20up%20custom%20ordering%20the%20tiles%20in%2