%20we%20have%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%20of%20my%20country%2C%20my%20state%20and%20my%20city.%20Javeria%20is%20equally%20overwhelmed.%20There%20had%20been%20a%20flood%20of%20congratulatory%20phone%20calls%2C%20visits%20by%20friends%20and%20even%20strangers%20to%20our%20residence%20since%20we%20arrived%20from%20Amritsar%20to%20Kolkata%20on%20Tuesday%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karachi%20resident%20crossed%20over%20into%20the%20Indian%20side%20from%20Attari%20in%20Amritsar%20district%20of%20Punjab%2C%20where%20she%20was%20welcomed%20by%20Khan%20and%20some%20members%20of%20his%20family%20to%20the%20beats%20of%20'dhol'%20on%20December%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20said%20apart%20from%20tucking%20into%20the%20typical%20city%20street%20food%20'phuchka'%20with%20her%2C%20he%20would%20love%20to%20take%20her%20%26quot%3Bto%20Park%20Street%20to%20introduce%20her%20to%20the%20eateries%20I%20love%20to%20visit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wants%20to%20see%20how%20she%20reacts%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20biryani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20the%20work%20routine%20for%20a%20few%20days%20to%20have%20quality%20time%20with%20family%20members%20and%20close%20friends%20only%20and%20then%20embark%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20explore%20the%20city.%20I%20know%20she%20will%20love%20my%20city%2C%20she%20has%20already%20started%20loving%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata-based%20businessman%20had%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20Khanum%20in%202018%20after%20seeing%20her%20photo%20on%20his%20mother's%20mobile.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20he%20had%20come%20home%20from%20Germany%20where%20he%20was%20studying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20looking%20forward%20to%20tying%20the%20knot%20with%20her%20in%20January%20(2024)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20said%20his%20friends%20from%20Germany%2C%20Africa%2C%20Spain%2C%20the%20USA%20and%20other%20countries%20are%20likely%20to%20attend%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanum%20had%20earlier%20told%20PTI%20that%20she%20was%20granted%20a%2045-day%20visa.%20She%20had%20tried%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20on%20two%20occasions%20but%20got%20lucky%20the%20third%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20said%20he%20is%20thankful%20to%20the%20central%20government%20for%20this.%20PTI%20SUS%20NN%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701971520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F0v5og14_javeria-khanum_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-puchka-biryani-on-the-menu-for-kolkata-mans-pakistani-bride-4643944%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistani%20woman%20Javeria%20Khanum%20who%20came%20to%20Kolkata%20to%20marry%20the%20man%20she%20loves%20is%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20warmth%20and%20hospitality%20of%20the%20people%20here%20and%20cannot%20wait%20to%20savour%20the%20famed%20street%20food%20'phuchka'%2C%20this%20city's%20version%20of%20'pani%20puri'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-puchka-biryani-on-the-menu-for-kolkata-mans-pakistani-bride-4643944%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-puchka-biryani-on-the-menu-for-kolkata-mans-pakistani-bride-4643944%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengali-puchka-biryani-on-the-menu-for-kolkata-mans-pakistani-bride-4643944%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20'spectacular%20announcements'%20in%20interim%20Budget%2C%20says%20FM%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701971059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F07%2Ffull%2F1701949769-6855.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fno-spectacular