F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebut%20nothing%20on%20that%20front%20has%20panned%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Many%20students%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20took%20their%20semester%20examinations.%20After%20months%20of%20waiting%20for%20any%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20on%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20promise%20to%20formulate%20an%20online%20education%20plan%2C%20Kuki%20students%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20hill%20areas%20opted%20for%20admission%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fkuki-students-look-to-the-rest-of-india-for-their-higher-studies%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Kannur%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDead%20bodies%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETribal%20leaders%20also%20denied%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20regarding%20the%20acceptance%20of%20dead%20bodies%2C%20questioning%20the%20committee%20for%20not%20meeting%20them%20and%20addressing%20their%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20COTU%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20taken%20on%20a%20tour%20by%20the%20state%20authorities%20who%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tribals%2C%20have%20assisted%20the%20assailants%2C%20has%20its%20own%20problems%20regarding%20who%20the%20committee%20is%20introduced%20to%20by%20state%20officials%20for%20interaction.%20We%20would%20recommend%20that%20after%20completing%20the%20tour%20organised%20by%20the%20state%2C%20the%20above%20mentioned%20tribal%20organisations%20be%20consulted%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20areas%20so%20that%20the%20committee%20may%20get%20accurate%20information%20from%20the%20tribal%20and%20victim%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%