class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20this%20will%20demoralise%20Congress%20star%20campaigners%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%20Priyanka.%20Will%20this%20defeat%20be%20a%20setback%20to%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20bid%20for%20over%20a%20year%20to%20challenge%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20communal%20and%20divisive%20agenda%3F%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20had%20revived%20much%20hope%20among%20all%20those%20who%20craved%20for%20the%20return%20of%20the%20times%20before%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20happier%2C%20more%20tolerant%20and%20accommodating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20thumping%20his%20chest%2C%20a%20triumphant%20Modi%20proudly%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEk%20akela%20kitnon%20ko%20bhari%20pad%20raha%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Will%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20be%20crushed%20by%20this%20defeat%2C%20or%20will%20it%20rise%20to%20face%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20Lone%20Ranger%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20many%20issues%20to%20be%20pondered%20while%20analysing%20this%20humiliating%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20gloating%20over%20the%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20for%20instance.%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20the%20shining%20star%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20billionaire%20club%2C%20whom%20Modi%20fondly%20nurtures%2C%20would%20also%20be%20exulting.%20Outgoing%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20had%20warned%20that%20a%20BJP%20victory%20would%20open%20the%20floodgates%20for%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20exploitation%20of%20this%20mineral-rich%20tribal%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMost%20Rajasthan%20watchers%20had%20pronounced%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20a%20lost%20cause%20much%20before%20elections%20were%20announced%2C%20and%20with%20some%20justification%2C%20because%20of%20the%20way%20in%20which%20Gehlot%20refused%20to%20share%20power%20with%20the%20young%2C%20promising%20and%20hard-working%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20whom%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20had%20sent%20to%20Rajasthan%20after%20its%20defeat%20in%202013%20to%20revive%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20president%2C%20he%20did%20creditable%20work%20in%20eastern%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20dominated%20by%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20Gujjar%20community.%20When%20the%20Congress%20offered%20Gehlot%20its%20national%20presidency%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20if%20it%20meant%20relinquishing%20Rajasthan%20to%20Pilot.%20People%20were%20witness%20to%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20lust%20for%20power%20and%20the%20humiliation%20of%20Pilot%2C%20and%20were%20sure%20to%20teach%20him%20a%20lesson.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20himself%20was%20sceptical%20of%20a%20victory%20in%20Rajasthan.%20So%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20not%20a%20shock%20like%20the%20debacle%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20It%20shows%20that%20if%20Gehlot%20and%20Pilot%20had%20worked%20together%20as%20a%20team%20for%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20have%20beaten%20the%20past%20trend%20of%20BJP%20alternating%20in%20office%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-2024-is-going-to-be-an-existential-fight-for-the-india-alliance%5C%22%3EWhy%202024%20Is%20Going%20to%20Be%20an%20Existential%20Fight%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20messing%20up%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20since%202018%2C%20when%20it%20chose%20that%20ageing%20has-been%20Kamal%20Nath%20to%20lead%20the%20party%20and%20be%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Even%20after%20the%20Congress%20won%20in%202018%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20refused%20to%20hand%20over%20his%20party%20post%20to%20rival%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20shortly%20after%20its%20formation%2C%20due%20to%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20more%20importantly%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20a%20Hindutva%20proponent%20and%20a%20moneybag%2C%20the%20wrong%20choice%20to%20lead%20a%20state%20with%20a%20large%20population%20of%20tribals%2C%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%20A%20very%20influential%20and%20assertive%20section%20of%20upper%20castes%20have%20held%20the%20reins%20of%20power%20all%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20caught%20between%20two%20contradictions.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20promising%20a%20caste%20census%20if%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20was%20an%20upper-caste%20Hindutva%20proponent.%20Besides%2C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20opening%20a%20%E2%80%98Mohabbat%20ki%20dukaan%E2%80%99%20with%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20tow%20lacked%20conviction%20and%20sounded%20hollow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPerhaps%20we%20should%20not%20entirely%20blame%20the%20Congress%20leadership.%20After%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20arrival%20on%20the%20national%20scene%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20so%20badly%20weakened%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20high%20command%20barely%20exists%20and%20for%20lack%20of%20it%2C%20its%20satraps%20have%20become%20a%20law%20unto%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20party%20high%20command%2C%20including%20Rahul%2C%20Sonia%20and%20Congress%20president%20Malikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20must%20share%20a%20considerable%20degree%20of%20blame.%20Having%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20forming%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Kharge%20abandoned%20the%20idea%20soon%2C%20when%20the%20time%20came%20to%20demonstrate%20unity%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20The%20results%20in%20these%20three%20states%20would%20not%20have%20been%20any%20worse%20than%20this.%20A%20victory%20could%20have%20been%20possible.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20it%20would%20have%20sent%20the%20message%20of%20a%20national%20alliance%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EProbably%20in%201988%2C%20V.P.%20Singh%20held%20a%20rally%20in%20Agra.%20There%20were%20many%20leaders%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20including%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal%20and%C2%A0%20N.T.%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20then%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%2C%20whose%20heavily%20accented%20Hindi%20was%20hard%20to%20understand.%20But%20that%20rally%20sent%20out%20the%20message%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20National%20Front.%20In%20the%201989%20elections%2C%20the%20National%20Front%20virtually%20drew%20a%20blank%20in%20the%20South%2C%20but%20Singh%20remained%20committed%20to%20it.%20His%20cabinet%20included%20Murasoli%20Maran%20of%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20as%20urban%20development%20minister%2C%20K.P.%20Unnikrishnan%20in%20charge%20of%20telecom%2C%20shipping%20and%20surface%20transport%2C%20and%20P.%20Upendra%20as%20information%20and%20broadcasting%20minister%2C%20all%20heading%20important%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20same%20principle%20was%20followed%20by%20subsequent%20national%20alliances%20like%20the%20United%20Front%20led%20by%20Deve%20Gowda.%20I.K.%20Gujral%2C%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%2C%20and%20even%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20brought%20together%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%2C%20all%20followed%20the%20pattern.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202004%20general%20elections%20led%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20despite%20stiff%20opposition%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20she%20struck%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20newly%20formed%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(now%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi)%20and%20gave%20it%20a%20place%20in%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20takes%20no%20time%20to%20announce%20a%20front%2C%20but%20it%20is%20much%20more%20difficult%20to%20keep%20it%20together.%20Like%20most%20Congressmen%2C%20Manmohan%20Singh%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20too%20pleased%20with%20some%20of%20his%20ministers%20from%20coalition%20parties.%20But%20Sonia%20kept%20them%20in%20good%20humour%20throughout.%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20should%20learn%20that%20lesson%20fast%20before%20the%20situation%20gets%20completely%20out%20of%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701937805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-defeat-turns-the-spotlight-on-indias-resilience%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20takes%20no%20time%20to%20announce%20a%20front%2C%20but%20it%20is%20much%20more%20difficult%20to%20keep%20it%20together.%20Having%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20forming%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Kharge%20abandoned%20the%20idea%20soon%2C%20when%20the%20time%20came%20to%20demonstrate%20unity%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-defeat-turns-the-spotlight-on-indias-resilience%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World-first%20trial%20finds%20arthritis%20drug%20may%20help%20treat%20type%201%20diabetes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701936240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F04%2F768x432%2Fskynews-diabetes-glucose_6119025.jpg%3F20230412122413%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworld-first-trial-finds-arthritis-drug-may-help-treat-type-1-diabetes-13024706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20world-first%20clinical%20trial%20has%20found%20a%20common%20drug%20used%20to%20treat%20rheumatoid%20arthritis%20can%20suppress%20the%20progression%20of%20type%201%20diabetes%20in%20recently%20diagnosed%20patients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A214%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fworld-first-trial-finds-arthritis-drug-may-help-treat-type-1-diabetes-13024706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworld-first-trial-finds-arthritis-drug-may-help-treat-type-1-diabetes-13024706%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fworld-first-trial-finds-arthritis-drug-may-help-treat-type-1-diabetes-13024706%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Witnessing%20Palestine%20in%20New%20York%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Watching%20India's%20Moral%20Vision%20Disappear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20to%20New%20York%20as%20a%20graduate%20student%20three%20years%20ago.%20These%20three%20years%20have%20been%20the%20most%20demanding%20and%20stimulating%20period%20of%20my%20academic%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20and%20joyous%20accidents%20of%20this%20journey%20has%20been%20my%20close%20friendship%20with%20fellow%20Arab%20students%20in%20this%20city.%20I%20have%20shared%20a%20house%20with%20a%20Syrian%20and%20a%20Palestinian%20here%20in%20Brooklyn%20and%20have%20grown%20to%20call%20it%20a%20home.%20I%20now%20make%20makloubeh%20with%20lal%20mirch%20and%20garam%20masala.%20Pita%20bread%20with%20zaatar%20and%20olive%20oil%20has%20become%20my%20go-to%20midnight%20snack.%20I%20have%20gotten%20drunk%20on%20arak%20and%20unsuccessfully%20danced%20dabke%20at%20parties.%20The%20Delhi%20boy%20in%20me%20has%20also%20learned%20to%20cuss%20in%20Arabic%20now.%20These%20friendships%20have%20made%20me%20realise%20how%20similar%20we%20are%20to%20each%20other%20as%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20best%20friend%20in%20the%20city%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20Palestinian%20Christian%20whose%20family%20was%20displaced%20from%20Jerusalem%20in%201948%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20exile%20ever%20since.%20My%20roommate%20is%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20family%20have%20to%20face%20the%20everyday%20humiliation%20of%20crossing%20Israeli%20checkpoints%20to%20travel%20in%20their%20own%20country.%20It%20did%20not%20start%20on%20October%207%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20hearing%20stories%20about%20the%20Israeli%20settler%20violence%20in%20occupied%20Palestine%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20I%20know%20people%20in%20this%20city%20whose%20houses%20have%20been%20bombed%2C%20and%20whose%20family%20members%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20arbitrarily%20arrested%2C%20and%20displaced%20in%20Palestine.%20I%20attach%20human%20faces%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Ramallah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20Jerusalem.%20I%20will%20not%20pretend%20to%20write%20from%20a%20neutral%20and%20distanced%20position%20today.%20Neutrality%20often%20helps%20the%20oppressor%2C%20not%20the%20oppressed.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Palestine%20has%20become%20as%20far%20and%20as%20close%20as%20India%2C%20in%20some%20ways.%20When%20I%20read%20the%20news%20from%20Gaza%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20hits%20me%20as%20if%20something%20horrible%20is%20unfolding%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20destruction%20of%20Gaza%20has%20shaken%20the%20world%20to%20the%20core.%20More%20than%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20including%2010%2C000%20women%20and%20children%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza.%20Another%2017%2C00%2C000%20people%20stand%20displaced.%20Numbers%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20the%20time%20you%20read%20this.%20Hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20universities%2C%20homes%2C%20refugee%20shelters%20and%20UN%20offices%20have%20been%20relentlessly%20bombed.%20A%20senior%20UN%20human%20rights%20expert%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F31%2Fun-official-resigns-israel-hamas-war-palestine-new-york%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Gaza%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter.%20Along%20with%20Gaza%2C%20all%20the%20rules%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20have%20been%20bombed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces.%20Amidst%20this%20destruction%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20for%20liberation%20has%20found%20renewed%20support%20across%20the%20globe.%20Millions%20have%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Berlin%2C%20Paris%2C%20Cairo%2C%20Amman%2C%20Stockholm%2C%20Amsterdam%2C%20Seoul%2C%20Johannesburg%2C%20Wellington%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Islamabad%2C%20Dhaka%2C%20Sao%20Paulo%2C%20Bogota%2C%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20Santiago%20and%20countless%20other%20cities%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20free%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Israel's%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-hamas-red-herring-evicting-palestinians-gaza%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20Goal%20of%20Eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20Red%20Herring%2C%20Evicting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20is%20the%20Real%20Aim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20New%20York%20has%20witnessed%20protests%20every%20single%20day%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months.%20New%20Yorkers%20of%20all%20colours%2C%20classes%2C%20nationalities%2C%20ethnicities%20and%20religious%20backgrounds%20have%20gathered%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20heart%20of%20the%20American%20empire%20reverberates%20with%20passionate%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9D%20Ceasefire%20now%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2