0with%20elements%20of%20regular%2C%20everyday%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20biopic%20on%20the%20maestro%20is%20in%20the%20making%20and%20actor%20Dhanush%20will%20reportedly%20essay%20the%20role.%20According%20to%20the%20reports%2C%20the%20film%20will%20go%20on%20floors%20in%202024%20and%20be%20released%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20trade%20analyst%20Manobala%20Vijayabalan%20confirmed%20the%20news%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fan-artiste-of-the-millennium-ilaiyaraaja-at-75%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20Artiste%20of%20the%20Millennium%3A%20Ilaiyaraaja%20at%2075%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Karthikeyan%20Damodaran%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20Published%20on%2010%20September%2C%202018%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmovies%2Fregional-cinema%2Fstory%2Fdhanush-to-play-isaignani-ilaiyaraaja-in-upcoming-biopic-2456654-2023-11-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Dhanush%20to%20play%20Isaignani%20Ilaiyaraaja%20in%20upcoming%20biopic%3F%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20on%201%20November%2C%202023%20Courtesy%20India%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700747511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhanush%20is%20set%20to%20play%20Ilaiyaraaja%20in%20his%20biopic.%20Here's%20the%20inspiring%20story%20of%20the%20legendary%20composer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.c